# NOTE: this file has no effect. Verified against SAM CLI 1.163.0 /
# aws-lambda-builders 1.65.0 — neither package references "samignore"
# anywhere; it was never a real exclude mechanism for `sam build`'s
# Python/pip CopySource step (only ever applied to the legacy raw-zip
# `sam package` flow, which this project doesn't use). CodeUri is the
# repo root, so `sam build` copies everything, including data/raw and
# test directories. See infra/deploy.sh, which prunes those paths from
# the build output before deploying. Keeping this file only so the next
# person doesn't reintroduce the same wrong assumption.
#
.git/
.claude/
.pytest_cache/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
frontend/
mining/tests/
api/tests/
infra/
data/raw/
data/output/
.env
